data.description: Discover this 2 story 4 bedroom 3 bath home offering a completely remodeled kitchen and entire first floor!  The stunning first floor has new Luxury vinyl plank flooring, new baseboards, fresh paint, new light fixtures and a new door entering the 3 season room. The new cabinets offer soft close doors, the huge island has a gorgeous butcher block counter and offers island seating.  It opens into the kitchen eating area and family room with a cozy brick fireplace!  The first floor also boasts a spacious living room with a formal dining area off of the kitchen. All 3 baths have been updated! You will find the good sized bedrooms upstairs along with an updated ensuite bath and hall bath.  The storage is phenomenal in this home and offers walk in attic area upstairs.  The backyard is great with a fence and nice, spacious shed. This qualifies for USDA financing. All stainless appliances stay (not warranted).    Come take a look!
